data.description: GOOD VIBES ONLY.......one step inside of my doors you will immediately be welcomed by my neutral colors and open floor plan.  My foyer will gracefully introduce you to my spacious great room that overlooks the kitchen.  If I must say so myself, you will never find many kitchens that will offer you the amenities that I do.  Not trying to brag, but when you have gorgeous granite counter tops, a new stainless steel dishwasher and refrigerator....I would consider myself competition.  Clearly I can tell you are already SOLD, but hold on there is more!!! I have a kitchen island that could easily accommodate the conversationalist of the family and there is still room for your kitchen table! The kitchen overlooks the fenced-in backyard, so of course the kids can play while dinner is being prepared.  Now let's venture over to my master bedroom and bath which is conveniently located off of the great room.  I also have a desirable split bedroom layout, so invite the in-laws for the weekend, because they will have their side of the house! With the holidays approaching, my backyard has been well-maintained with an adorable patio.  My current owners have already have an established above ground garden and a detached storage shed awaiting you. I am conveniently located within 14 miles of Maxwell AFB and the local downtown area.  What more can I say, but call the realtor who knows me the best.  You know the one with the sign in my yard!
